    <entry>
      <title>XXE(外部实体注入)</title>
      <link href="/2024/01/19/XXE/"/>
      <url>/2024/01/19/XXE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- imag形式<img src="XXE/f.jpg">中括号形式 ![log](XXE/f.jpg)大括号形式 --><h1>xml前置知识</h1>先看一个简单的例子，看实体是如何工作的：<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">&quot;1.0&quot;</span>?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">Person</span>[</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">    <span class="meta">&lt;!ENTITY <span class="keyword">name</span> <span class="string">&quot;John&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">]&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Person</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">name</span>&gt;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;name;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">name</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">age</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">age</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">Person</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>用浏览器解析结果：<img src="/mangww.github.io/2024/01/19/XXE/lizi.png">  <p>可以看到&name;的位置被替换为了Jhon</p><h2>存在三种类型实体<h3>general(通用型)<h3>paramter(参数型)</h3>此类实体只允许DTD中使用，并且它们灵活。例如创建一个值为另一个实体的实体：<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!ENTITY % <span class="keyword">outer</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;!ENTITY inner &#x27;John&#x27;&gt;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3>predefined(预定义型)</h3>特定的几种:<img src="/mangww.github.io/2024/01/19/XXE/shiti.png">  </h3></h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>flask session伪造</title>
      <link href="/2023/12/20/flask-session%E4%BC%AA%E9%80%A0/"/>
      <url>/2023/12/20/flask-session%E4%BC%AA%E9%80%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用脚本flask-session-cookie-manager  </p><p>脚本有解密、加密两种功能，具体用法如下：</p><p>解密:<br>python3 flask_session_manager3.py decode -c “要解密的session值” -s “SECRET_KEY”</p><p>加密:<br>python3 flask_session_manager.py3 encode -s “SECRET_KEY” -t “要加密的session值”</p><p>SECRET_KEY指的是密钥</p><p>session格式例如:<br>eyJuYW1lIjoiYWRtaW4ifQ.ZYHJcg.gRqmTkP0GuXE3r7ctFopx7ShICE</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
